The paper discusses the use of an Intrusion Detection System (IDS) to protect UASs against security attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The IDS is inspired by the human immune system (HIS), which involves the use of machine learning and pattern recognition techniques, falling under the categories of network security (cs.NI), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the testing and validation of the system, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
